response.original_title: No soy súper, pero puedo ser tu héroe
response.overview: Christopher is tormented by an imaginary monster and hallucinations. When he arrives home, he finds himself face-to-face with Luna, his ex-girlfriend. Christopher is unsure whether she is real or an illusion, but decides to spend the day with her.
response.title: No soy súper, pero puedo ser tu héroe
